data.description: Contract BUSTED. Their loss is your gainl Price IMPROVEMENT . No fault to owner . Buyers financing fell through.Dynamic is and understatement . 5 Acres with Beautiful landscaping / mature trees / hills and also flat areas. Warehouse / Shop in back with privacy fence w 3 phase electric capabilities . Lots of different sections where family gatherings and memories can be made. Lined with Pine trees on corner of back of property. Additional Barn for storage or home office . Barn does have full electricity and attic for storage. House has been updated and upgraded. Freshly painted recently , hand scraped hardwood floors / granite counter tops in kitchen- Marble in bathrooms - Carpet areas are upgraded carpet..Even has an adorable Chicken coupe that can be very versatile  Truly an Awesome property! If you are looking for privacy yet close to all city immunities THIS IS IT !  Truly words can not describe this timeless beauty. Come create your Own Oasis. The beauty and the peaceful scenery can not be described in words.... Come see yourself .
